data.description: Newly built ranch style home in the heart of Ave Maria City. This home features a grande entrance opening up to an open concept living area and kitchen made for an entertainers dream including an oversized stone countertop with modern finishes and fully equipped with stainless steel appliances. The oversized primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom with separate tub and shower and toilet closet, leading into a expansive walk in closet. The two additional bedrooms connects with a jack and jill bathroom. The fourth bedroom located near the entrance can also be great option for an office and/or play room. Two-Car Garage with plenty of driveway parking and an open backyard. The community amenities include a resort-style clubhouse, pool, fitness center and playground.
